    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This FYI RFC answers the question, "What is the Internet?" and is produced by the User Services Working Group of the Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF).  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
